   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Purpose     : V2 Class add/edit form page. Uses the V2 PageTemplateV2
                 primitive instead of deprecated FormPageV2 and FormSectionV2.
                 Delegates form state and API calls to ClassFormViewModelV2.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  2026-03-21  Initial implementation (Phase 7).
     - 1.0.1  2026-03-25  Removed invalid V2 component imports.
     - 1.1.0  2026-03-26  Replaced FormPageV2 + FormSectionV2 with PageTemplateV2.
                          Updated namespace and layout. Preserved all bindings
                          and ViewModel logic.
     - (bumped)  2026-04-04  Phase 3 Stabilisation Issue 2: changed @layout from BaseLayoutV2 to MainLayoutV2 so all module pages use the canonical V2 shell layout with correct fixed-header padding.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Notes       :
